&lt;a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/52922060/rgeos-package-installation-error-on-linux-google-compute-instance-r">answer on &lt;i class="fa fa-stack-overflow" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> claiming that it is a bug. The build indeed fails for &lt;a href="https://cran.r-project.org/web/checks/check_results_rgeos.html">r-release-linux-x86_64&lt;/a>
but there is no more details&amp;hellip; So, as recommended in the answer, I downgraded
to version 0.3-28:&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>